We got so many questions from you guys! Thanks for your participation! 🥲 we got a lot of similar questions so we had to put some of them together and change it into a video recording. This is our first time recording a Q&A session with our Eggbun Coach, so please understand why there may be mistakes.🙏
If you have any other questions, DM us anytime! And if you enjoyed the video, please let us know, and then we will continue making more of these!
Thank you for watching and see you guys in class!👍👍

node.text:
Don’t miss the registration for our Basic Korean class! We’re starting on September 3rd 🤗 (Join now and get an Early Bird discount!🐣
As any other Basic Korean class, this class is run for 8-weeks offering daily homework assignments and daily topics to study with the Eggbun app. Students get daily feedback from their Eggbun Coach and once in two weeks students are having a group Zoom call class with their teacher to practice what they’ve learned during the class and have some small talk in Korean 😊
Join us and let’s have fun studying Korean together!
✔Click the link in our bio to learn more details about the class! (price, curriculum, etc.). The name of the link: “Basic Korean with Lainy”

*The class is recommended for Beginner level students, who can read Korean and know some Korean ground basics (e.g. markers)
